<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1436,1621,1724]" pageId="6" pageNumber="47">
Two collections were cited by 
<bibRefCitation author="Baker, J. G." box="[507,662,1621,1647]" pageId="6" pageNumber="47" pagination="1 - 134" refId="ref6447" refString="Baker, J. G. (1882) Compositae. III. Asteroideae, Inuloideae. In: Martius, C. F. P. † &amp; Eichler, A. G. (eds). Flora brasiliensis enumeratio plantarum in Brasilia hactenus detectarum quas suis aliorumque botanicorum studiis descriptas et methodo naturali digestas partim icone illustratas 6: 1 - 134. Monachii, Lipsiae: Fleischer." type="journal article" year="1882">Baker (1882)</bibRefCitation>
in the description of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Baker" authorityYear="1882" box="[910,1433,1621,1647]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Baccharis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="6" pageNumber="47" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="tarchonanthoides" variety="integrifolia">
<emphasis box="[910,1240,1621,1646]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="47">Baccharis tarchonanthoides</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis box="[1297,1433,1621,1646]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="47">integrifolia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis box="[1432,1436,1621,1646]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="47">.</emphasis>
Since none has been found so far, a 
<typeStatus box="[596,707,1660,1686]" pageId="6" pageNumber="47">lectotype</typeStatus>
cannot be designated here. The description provided in the protologue agrees with 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Gardner" authorityYear="1848" box="[425,605,1699,1724]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Baccharis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="6" pageNumber="47" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="lychnophora">
<emphasis box="[425,605,1699,1724]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="47">B. lychnophora</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Barroso, G. M." box="[661,837,1698,1724]" pageId="6" pageNumber="47" pagination="1 - 281" refId="ref6519" refString="Barroso, G. M. (1976) Subtribo Baccharidinae Hoffman. Estudo das especies ocorrentes no Brasil. Rodriguesia 28: 1 - 281." type="journal article" year="1976">Barroso (1976)</bibRefCitation>
recognized this name as a synonym of this species.
</paragraph>
